text: Oksana Andreyevna Voevodina (; born 10 July 1992 in Astrakhan), also known as Rihana Oksana Gorbatenko (Рихана Оксана Горбатенко) and Xenia Diaghileva or Ksenia Dyagileva (Ксения Дягилева), is a Russian model and Miss Moscow 2015 beauty pageant winner. On 22 November 2018, Voevodina married Sultan Muhammad V of Kelantan, who is also the 15th Yang di-Pertuan Agong (King) of Malaysia. Oksana gave birth of their son Tengku Ismail Leon Petra bin Tengku Muhammad V Faris Petra on 21 May 2019. On 22 June 2019, Muhammad V divorced Voevodina. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Russian models Category:People from Astrakhan
